text: Takatomo Enoki from the Nippon Telegraph and Telephone Corporation, NTT, Atsugi-shi, Kanagawa, Japan was named Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for contributions to compound semiconductor high speed integrated circuits for optical and wireless communication systems. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Takatomo Enoki
